/**
 * Shared vehicle computation utilities used by both ExcelDataSource
 * and DataverseDataSource.
 *
 * All functions here are pure — they operate on Vehicle[] and pricing
 * data passed in as arguments, so any IDataSource implementation can
 * reuse them.
 */

